back_droom_001

This place is what you would call a happening bar.
The main idea is for the customers to have fun
together, but if you pay, you can request a staff
member to accompany you.

Paying money only buys you time, and sexual
activity requires consent. Whether or not you can
have a physical relationship depends on
negotiation or additional payment.

And now Kuno has been requested. Curious, I
decided to observe the situation.
$gameVariables._data[1][76] = '服'//服装(服or裸)

It seems like they're just drinking and talking
together. Prae said that it's better not to have a
relationship on the first request because the
value of suddenly being embraced would decrease.

I think it's questionable whether this format of
the bar would work, but it might be because the
customers are mostly men.

I continued watching afterwards, but it seems like
they just ended up drinking together.
